Print the following pattern for the given N number of rows.
Pattern for N = 4
*
**
***
****
Input format :
Integer N (Total no. of rows)
Output format :
Pattern in N lines



Solution:
import java.util.Scanner;
public class Solution {


	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Scanner s=new Scanner(System.in);
        
int n=s.nextInt();

        int i, j;
        for(i=0; i<n; i++)
        {
            for(j=0; j<=i; j++)
            {
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
	
